<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Situs tidak dapat dijangkau</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --bg-color: #202124;
            --text-main: #e8eaed;
            --text-sub: #9aa0a6;
            --button-bg: #8ab4f8;
            --button-text: #202124;
        }

        body {
            background-color: var(--bg-color);
            color: var(--text-main);
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, sans-serif;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 400px;
            width: 100%;
            text-align: left;
        }

        .icon {
            width: 72px;
            height: 72px;
            margin-bottom: 35px;
            color: var(--text-sub);
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 22px;
            font-weight: 400;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            line-height: 1.3;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: var(--text-sub);
            line-height: 1.5;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }

        .error-code {
            font-size: 12px;
            margin-top: 25px;
            color: var(--text-sub);
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .btn-reload {
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 40px;
            width: calc(100% - 40px);
            max-width: 360px;
            background-color: var(--button-bg);
            color: var(--button-text);
            border: none;
            padding: 12px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 600;
            cursor: pointer;
            text-align: center;
            transition: opacity 0.2s;
        }

        .btn-reload:active {
            opacity: 0.7;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="container">
        <svg class="icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
            <path d="M14 2H6c-1.1 0-1.99.9-1.99 2L4 20c0 1.1.89 2 1.99 2H18c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2V8l-6-6zM6 20V4h7v5h5v11H6zm10-9h-1.5c-.28 0-.5.22-.5.5v1c0 .28.22.5.5.5h1.5c.28 0 .5-.22.5-.5v-1c0-.28-.22-.5-.5-.5zm-7.5 0H7c-.28 0-.5.22-.5.5v1c0 .28.22.5.5.5h1.5c.28 0 .5-.22.5-.5v-1c0-.28-.22-.5-.5-.5zm2.5 5c-1.66 0-3 1.34-3 3h6c0-1.66-1.34-3-3-3z"/>
        </svg>

        <h1>Situs ini tidak dapat dijangkau</h1>
        
        <p>Periksa apakah ada kesalahan ketik di <strong><%= domainName %></strong>.</p>
        
        <div class="error-code">
            <%= errorCode %>
        </div>
    </div>

    <button class="btn-reload" onclick="location.reload()">Muat ulang</button>

</body>
</html>
